ith, <ORGANIZATION> Congress </ORGANIZATION> after <ORGANIZATION> Congress </ORGANIZATION>, that they've done a pretty good job of it.'' So much for cynicism. The film was underwritten by the information industry giant <ORGANIZATION> Ameritech </ORGANIZATION> and co-produced by <ORGANIZATION> WETA </ORGANIZATION> of <LOCATION> Washington </LOCATION> and Florentine Films. <PERSON> Byrd </PERSON>'s book, `` The <ORGANIZATION> Senate </ORGANIZATION>, 1789-1989,'' is available from the <ORGANIZATION> Government </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Printing </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Office </ORGANIZATION> in <LOCATION> Washington </LOCATION> and its depositories around the country for $ 55.
