 another incident, <PERSON> Klaas </PERSON> <PERSON> de </PERSON> <PERSON> Jonge </PERSON>, a Dutch citizen accused of smuggling weapons for the <ORGANIZATION> African </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> National </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Congress </ORGANIZATION> guerrilla movement, took refuge in the Dutch Consulate in <LOCATION> Pretoria </LOCATION> for more than two years before he was returned to the <LOCATION> Netherlands </LOCATION> in September 1987 in an exchange involving prisoners in four countries.
