ected to be rolled out to a <LOCATION> Cape </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Canaveral </LOCATION> launch pad Wednesday for its scheduled April 28 liftoff. The Atlantis astronauts will deploy a probe that will map the surface of <PERSON> Venus </PERSON>.
